PKG_SHORTDESC="HTTP::Request::Common - Construct common HTTP::Request objects"
PKG_LONGDESC="This module provide functions that return newly created HTTP::Request objects. These functions are usually more convenient to use than the standard HTTP::Request constructor for the most common requests."
